  "description": "Relocate is mod that adds new redstone-like Blocks based on Copper and Tuff.",
  "body": "<p><img style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/null/description_ddfcb294-28e5-4e6d-97fe-be37b0785f93.png\" alt=\"Relocate Banner\" width=\"585\" height=\"275\"></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align:center\">Weclome to Relocate!</h1>\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">Relocate is mod that adds redstone-like blocks based on Trial Chambers theme. It is designed to be<strong> easy to understand</strong>, just <strong>hover over block</strong> and <strong>hold shift</strong>, <strong>build-in tooltips will help you</strong>!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">For better experience, download <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/jei\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Just Enough Items (JEI)</a> mod.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">In game gifs:</p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/null/description_1b548bab-486b-4cfe-a938-8217f5d18085.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"222\" height=\"139\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/null/description_fa2f76ac-f82e-4f6d-beea-8794baeb014b.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"222\" height=\"139\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/null/description_de628e85-40f3-45a8-9303-fe139b8a10c6.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"222\" height=\"139\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/null/description_7f36a623-d81c-4d08-9c85-fb7d373dd106.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"222\" height=\"500\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/null/description_712cccba-36eb-423c-9bea-ad9bd903fd96.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"222\" height=\"139\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/null/description_d3786c9f-71e2-44d0-a043-1fc4493e36b0.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"222\" height=\"139\">&nbsp; &nbsp; <img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/null/description_aa90c56a-1b72-493a-bb14-f3402f8afe1e.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"222\" height=\"139\"></p>\n</div>\n    </div>",
